definitions.definition: A main road or highway , especially in ancient Rome. (Mainly used in set phrases, below.)
A small hole in a printed circuit board filled with metal which connects two or more layers .
An electrical connection which connects two or more layers on a printed circuit board or an integrated circuit .

main_definition: A main road or highway , especially in ancient Rome. (Mainly used in set phrases, below.)
